data.description: This spacious townhouse is a real gem in the Foxfire Subdivision you don’t want to miss! The open floor plan with raised ceilings provides plenty of room for all your furniture! Stainless steel appliances in the eat-in kitchen, plenty of solid oak wood cabinets, pantry, and an inviting passthrough from kitchen to family room make conversations easy with guests. The dining room area adjacent to the kitchen can double as additional living room space. The main ensuite has gorgeous walk-in closet organizers, and a large ensuite bath with dual vanity sinks, jetted tub, and separate shower. The fenced in backyard with patio and ample yard space is perfect to entertain!
